---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Air Quality Sensors | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Monitor air quality, temperature, humidity, CO2, and VOCs in real time with Verkada environmental sensors. Cloud-managed with instant alerts through Blue Cap IT.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Air Quality</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Air Quality <span class="grad">Sensors</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">Monitor indoor air quality in real time. Track particulate matter, CO₂, humidity, temperature, and VOCs — all from your Verkada Command dashboard.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Sensor Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-grid-2">
          <img src="/240220_AirQuality_Family_Iso.png" alt="Verkada Air Quality Sensors"/>
          <img src="/air-quality-hero.png" alt="Verkada Environmental Sensor"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Verkada Sensors</div>
        <h2>See It. <span class="grad">Sense It.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual">
            <img src="/verkada/air-quality/wall-mount-sensor.png" alt="Verkada BC51 wall mount sensor" style="max-width:100%;max-height:320px;border-radius:8px;" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Designed for Any Environment</h3>
            <p>Compact wall-mounted sensors that blend into any space. Monitor air quality, temperature, humidity, and more without disrupting your environment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual">
            <img src="/verkada/air-quality/sensor-dashboard.png" alt="Verkada sensor dashboard view" style="max-width:100%;max-height:320px;border-radius:8px;" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Real-Time Dashboard</h3>
            <p>View all sensor readings at a glance from Verkada Command. Set custom thresholds and receive instant alerts when conditions change.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 3.5rem;">
        <div class="section-label">What We Monitor</div>
        <h2>Know Your Environment,<br/><span class="grad">Before It's a Problem.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">🌡️</div><h3>Temperature &amp; Humidity</h3><p>Protect server rooms, storage areas, and sensitive equipment with continuous monitoring and instant threshold alerts. 90-day historical data included.</p></div>
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">💨</div><h3>Air Quality (IAQ)</h3><p>Monitor CO2, VOC, PM2.5 particulates, and humidity levels. Ideal for offices, schools, and healthcare environments focused on occupant health.</p></div>
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">💧</div><h3>Water Leak Detection</h3><p>Detect water intrusion before it causes damage. Place sensors under HVAC units, near pipes, and in server rooms for early warning alerts.</p></div>
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">🏃</div><h3>Motion Detection</h3><p>Passive infrared (PIR) motion sensors that integrate directly with your camera system and access control — perfect for after-hours security triggers.</p></div>
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">🚪</div><h3>Door &amp; Window Contacts</h3><p>Know instantly when any door or window is opened or left ajar. Works in tandem with alarms and access control for complete perimeter awareness.</p></div>
        <div class="product-card"><div class="pcard-icon">📊</div><h3>Unified Dashboard</h3><p>All sensor data lives in Verkada Command alongside your cameras and access control. One login, one view, complete situational awareness.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Protect What Matters</div>
    <h2>Add Verkada Sensors to Your<br/><span class="grad">Security Platform</span></h2>
    <p>Blue Cap IT will help you select the right sensor mix for your facility and integrate everything into your existing Verkada system.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Sensor Consultation</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
